<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Successful - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894 0%, #00cec9 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .success-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894 0%, #00cec9 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .success-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .receipt-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .receipt-box h3 {
            color: #333333;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .receipt-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .receipt-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>Great news! Your payment has been processed successfully. Your Engagematic subscription is now active.</p>

            <div class="success-box">
                <h3>Payment Confirmed</h3>
                <div class="amount"><%= amount || '₹649' %></div>
                <div style="margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.9;">Transaction ID: <%= transactionId || 'N/A' %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="receipt-box">
                <h3>Payment Details</h3>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span>Plan:</span>
                    <span><%= plan || 'Pro Plan' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span>Amount:</span>
                    <span><%= amount || '₹649' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span>Payment Date:</span>
                    <span><%= paymentDate || new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span>Next Billing:</span>
                    <span><%= nextBillingDate || 'Next month' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span>Status:</span>
                    <span style="color: #00b894;">Active</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Full access to all premium features</li>
                <li>Unlimited content generation</li>
                <li>Priority support</li>
                <li>Advanced analytics</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Go to Dashboard →
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">A receipt has been sent to your email. You can also download it from your account settings.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for your continued support! We're excited to help you grow your LinkedIn presence.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

